target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/694890328273346560</a><br />\n<br />\n事實係...Trump係2016屌過Ted Cruz 出千 要重選"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T07:32:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/694879900256354304\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F694879900256354304&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUncTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=a7d3bde6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F694879900256354304&h=df682a99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/694879900256354304</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T07:37:00.000Z","msg":"Ted Cruz 果次只係謹謹贏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T07:37:56.000Z","msg":"ted cruz 茶檔領袖之一"},{"pid":"5afb8583a0fdb1ddee6e14141c94e4816672e3cc","tid":2297282,"uid":377617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T07:39:41.000Z","msg":"呢條友應該唸住最算侵輸左選舉都會繼續告落去"},{"pid":"8576c8de42a9229ae1fde35d91e31a2450fdcaff","tid":2297282,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T07:40:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f4d6d6601480c3f174052c1e96459b7b2afda3c","tid":2297282,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T07:43:35.000Z","msg":"川皇必勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a47b1e5679d98f7da9c5e2089bf09e0e8f59457c","tid":2297282,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T07:46:40.000Z","msg":"七傷拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c612947b6ae18e3b65cc60bc3be854fe70127e70","tid":2297282,"uid":308915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T08:12:27.000Z","msg":"[慎防左膠帶風向］鮑威爾代表美國人控告選舉舞弊，並非代表侵侵團隊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2296914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2296914</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[11月23號]美國大選新聞總匯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2297112\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2297112</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d5a9e50e53ef3f1c3d0cd8577e28638aef43d494","tid":2297282,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T12:25:20.000Z","msg":"另外有消息指想避免涉及dominion 嘅財團控告鮑威爾誹謗 , 而影響侵侵連任 , 所以獨立出黎"},{"pid":"7b062046af1e1d6cef37c90f17ecb14505274d60","tid":2297282,"uid":266503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T12:31:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/newsmax/status/1330829713095471104?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnewsmax%2Fstatus%2F1330829713095471104%3Fs%3D21&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUncTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=6c777dd9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnewsmax%2Fstatus%2F1330829713095471104%3Fs%3D21&h=5a80c098\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/newsmax/status/1330829713095471104?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"85b2b51a60551bb72c215859bc205bc3c3351016","tid":2297282,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T12:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f85930c4ec9624147bbbc580a50920af83e966b6","tid":2297282,"uid":191189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T12:34:11.000Z","msg":"仲似為fed 果個鮑威爾"},{"pid":"f2626fd9b92a2051324a473cadd72c83687010b3","tid":2297282,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T02:09:01.000Z","msg":"又玩標題黨 帶風向<br />\n明明內文都講緊司法部 CIA有人知道舞弊 <span class=\"red\">但係侵控制唔哂全部人</span><br />\n你條撚樣就屈做「侵內部政府有份(造成/容許)」？<br />\n<br />\n咁真係萬能key<br />\n侵在任期間出咩事，就算係敵對派系搞屎棍，都可以屈做侵政府有份<br />\n<br />\n已經第2次捉到你隻垃圾標題黨 想帶風向"}]}